{"pid":"7e04c1f9ff35bb3a6d5cf1da4503ee9b1d8a2882","tid":1368131,"uid":274265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e627960a24232311044447fee32954a61c79522a","tid":1368131,"uid":234414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"咁即係要小心有人混入製造混亂"},{"pid":"10eee3b3fb65def86173f01916456a1956e1ae55","tid":1368131,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f99f15304a43d7965b10c130a65e482f73fc2c","tid":1368131,"uid":189799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"23歲男子梁X添，他涉嫌襲擊2名警務人員。案中2名便衣警員被示威者包圍、拳打腳踢及用雨傘攻擊頭及身體不同部位，致身體嚴重受傷，警方指會全力追查案件，不排除有更多人被捕，對違法行為會追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，梁報稱無業，疑有黑幫背景及販毒案底，於2011年3月曾因示威衝突被警方拘捕，與部分泛民議員有密切聯繫。他除涉及今次沙田衝突外，亦疑涉及於本月21日的衝擊中聯辦及在信德中心與警方對抗，另涉及其他多次衝擊行動。<br />\n<br />\n中左1樣"},{"pid":"bf49a463d68b1e045703f6a7d4512799c6c4a597","tid":1368131,"uid":271786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:28:43.000Z","msg":"起碼要招15-20名絲主力做拍攝，有任何事情發生要盡快退後重點拍攝，要確保電話有足夠電力及記憶體進行高清拍攝。就算自衛都要有足夠證據，以證清白，提防鄉黑警合謀大做文章。"},{"pid":"16a8e3ec5abc0ed086fb475bd674317d32f35903","tid":1368131,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e627960a24232311044447fee32954a61c79522a","tid":1368131,"uid":234414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"咁即係要小心有人混入製造混亂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"無錯，便衣黑社會咁耐以嚟都見過唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b7ad6cd9210ea64f82456df2a85091e05af8e7","tid":1368131,