":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f0b0e4acf84c08e0e3d6f6b7a54a8bb8bace8d","tid":1368131,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97719d56bb91642367c84bdc6fed9a8a1b950353","tid":1368131,"uid":278029,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:07:43.000Z","msg":"推，大家記得自己係為公義自由而行事，勿忘初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"一定會有黑幫著全黑！要做好準備！"},{"pid":"fcfad0ca2ad78c0ae16edfeae4a5e23f5ae2768e","tid":1368131,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3ea8eb9b0142ae588e2042690f6fc1ebedaab87","tid":1368131,"uid":190604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a1901c3c9c0c36a46a05eb12cb6d332c418ab53","tid":1368131,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e853891cf805f62e4043ece7348b5ccf71337232","tid":1368131,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"43ee2bbd6d9168d40c618895f5f8e5e71632920b","tid":1368131,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc551fa7adcbe716a2bd327eb8d246c318ed9535","tid":1368131,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:06:12.000Z","msg":"【一班AO的分享】<br />\n<br />\n你好，我哋係一班在政府各部門的AO，在此想補充更多的資料。<br />\n<br />\n最讓政府頭痛的，是一路以來，示威者的行動雖然涉及暴力，越趨激進，但從來都沒有踩中&ldquo;不波及無辜，不危及人身安全&rdquo;的底線，因此他們希望藉此惹來民意反彈的計劃終告失敗。<br />\n<br />\n但政府沒有因此死心，他們仍舊以奪回民意為先，今次他們希望透過利用網絡水軍，進一步激化示威者與鄉民間的對立，務求示威時的暴力會進一步升級，踩中上述所提及的底線, 並進一步抹黑這班示威者已走火入魔，與白衣人無異。<br />\n<br />\n他們更計劃引爆波及無辜的衝突後，進一步透過&lsquo;披露&rsquo;這群示威者有黑社會背景，進一步讓媒體不斷將事情發酵，讓普遍市民有&ldquo;示威已慢慢變成黑幫仇殺&rdquo;的印象，令普遍市民因為怕死而不再參與示威遊行，進一步削弱他們的力量，然後就開始清算。<br />\n<br />\n所以，這應該讓各位進一步明白網絡水軍的作用及他們往後的盤算，相信以你們的智慧，應該知道暴力的底線去到哪裡，知道怎樣佈局方能致勝，加油。<br />\n#AO #政務主任<br />\n<br />\n提交時間：2019/7/26 下午7:28<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/492354117860377/posts/724438314651955?s=100001713679889&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F492354117860377%2Fposts%2F724438314651955%3Fs%3D100001713679889%26sfns%3Dmo&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=940c80d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/492354117860377/posts/724438314651955?s=100001713679889&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保護身邊的人，保護真香港人，齊上齊落呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aea85c4a783c8c3fa790f00e3f5f632302f614","tid":1368131,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無野做就黎機場啦，前線叫到無力勒</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368273</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de95e4f1d0f05f963f2278b18a5693a2533d9afb","tid":1368131,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89aea85c4a783c8c3fa790f00e3f5f632302f614","tid":1368131,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無野做就黎機場啦，前線叫到無力勒</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368273</a><br /